何袭击的准备以色列对袭击“做出严厉回应” ■ 卡塔尔总理：停火谈判正处于“微妙阶段” ■ 战争已过去 194 天，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 17:20:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-194-hezbollah-wounds-at-least-18-in-missile-attack-on-north-israel/0000018e-ed03-dbb3-a3bf-fdcf89fe0000</guid></item><item><title>对于 10 月 7 日逃离哈马斯的以色列人来说，高速公路变成了死亡陷阱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/for-israelis-fleeing-hamas-on-october-7-highways-turned-into-death-traps/0000018e-e196-d052-a78f-e5d690780000</link><description>因巴尔开车去打架，尽管他的女朋友恳求他不要这么做。莎妮设法与她的祖父进行了最后一次视频通话。他们只是加沙边境附近道路上无法躲避哈马斯的 250 多人中的两人</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 16:34:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/for-israelis-fleeing-hamas-on-october-7-highways-turned-into-death-traps/0000018e-e196-d052-a78f-e5d690780000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军预备役人员情况危急，四人在无人机和导弹对北部的袭击中受重伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/idf-reservist-in-critical-condition-4-seriously-wounded-in-drone-rocket-attack-on-north/0000018e-ec8c-daad-a3de-eebfd45c0000</link><description>一架无人机和反坦克导弹袭击以色列北部阿拉伯阿拉姆谢的建筑物，造成 18 人受伤 ■ 以色列军队正在调查为何没有警报器警告无人机袭击</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 16:26:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/idf-reservist-in-critical-condition-4-seriously-wounded-in-drone-rocket-attack-on-north/0000018e-ec8c-daad-a3de-eebfd45c0000</guid></item><item><title>雷切尔·戈德堡-波林 (Rachel Goldberg-Polin) 的儿子赫什 (Hersh) 在加沙被扣为人质，入选《时代》杂志 100 名最具影响力人物名单</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/mother-of-israeli-held-in-gaza-named-to-time-magazines-100-most-influential-people-list/0000018e-ecaa-dbb3-a3bf-fdef93e40000</link><description>戈德堡-波林 23 岁的儿子赫什 (Hersh) 拥有美国和以色列双重国籍，于 10 月 7 日在诺瓦音乐节上被绑架。《时代》杂志的简介将她描述为“人质及其家人最引人注目的倡导者之一”</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 16:19:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/mother-of-israeli-held-in-gaza-named-to-time-magazines-100-most-influential-people-list/0000018e-ecaa-dbb3-a3bf-fdef93e40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列预计年底前将有8000名安全人员遭受心理伤害</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/health/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-expects-8-000-security-personnel-with-psychological-injuries-by-years-end/0000018e-ec39-d8eb-af8e-fdff5f000000</link><description>自10月7日以来，以色列国防部康复部门已收治7209名受伤士兵，其中约三分之一患有心理损伤，包括焦虑、抑郁、创伤后应激障碍、适应问题、沟通困难和精神病状态</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 15:07:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/health/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-expects-8-000-security-personnel-with-psychological-injuries-by-years-end/0000018e-ec39-d8eb-af8e-fdff5f000000</guid></item><item><title>学生处于以色列麦卡锡主义的最前沿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-17/ty-article-opinion/.premium/students-are-at-the-forefront-of-israeli-mccarthyism/0000018e-e5fa-de97-a5bf-f5fad4e80000</link><description>在以色列，学生们并没有像其他国家的学生那样扮演抵抗、反叛和挑战惯例的角色，而是领导着审查制度</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 12:57:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-17/ty-article-opinion/.premium/students-are-at-the-forefront-of-israeli-mccarthyism/0000018e-e5fa-de97-a5bf-f5fad4e80000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的战时内阁失去控制，可能导致以色列陷入地区战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-war-cabinet-has-lost-control-and-could-lead-israel-into-a-regional-war/0000018e-ebbb-d8eb-af8e-fbffd6fe0000</link><description>内阁部长们认为，他们未能看到伊朗的导弹和无人机袭击的答案就是进行报复——随着内塔尼亚胡联盟的压力越来越大，他的喋喋不休可能是唯一可以避免鲁莽反应的办法</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 12:25:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-war-cabinet-has-lost-control-and-could-lead-israel-into-a-regional-war/0000018e-ebbb-d8eb-af8e-fbffd6fe0000</guid></item><item><title>两名巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸与以色列定居者的冲突中被枪杀。无人被拘留</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/two-palestinians-were-fatally-shot-in-a-clash-with-west-bank-settlers-no-one-was-detained/0000018e-e8d0-dba7-a3ee-fcd9a9110000</link><description>纳布卢斯以南巴勒斯坦人和以色列定居者之间冲突的目击者称，士兵当时在场，但直到枪击结束后才采取行动。将尸体带到以色列进行尸检可能有助于将子弹与现场人员进行匹配</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 11:41:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/two-palestinians-were-fatally-shot-in-a-clash-with-west-bank-settlers-no-one-was-detained/0000018e-e8d0-dba7-a3ee-fcd9a9110000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗严厉打击头巾法；警方拍摄到当街袭击妇女的画面</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/iran-cracks-down-on-hijab-law-police-filmed-attacking-women-in-the-street/0000018e-eb79-d35c-a39e-fb7b15160000</link><description>据伊朗当地媒体报道，新的执法阶段尚未正式宣布，尽管最近在社交媒体上流传的视频显示，妇女遭到身穿制服的警卫的暴力袭击</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 10:41:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/iran-cracks-down-on-hijab-law-police-filmed-attacking-women-in-the-street/0000018e-eb79-d35c-a39e-fb7b15160000</guid></item><item><title>与以色列和美国结盟打击伊朗的阿拉伯国家现在面临后果</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/arab-states-that-allied-with-israel-and-u-s-for-iran-attack-now-face-consequences/0000018e-eb42-d35c-a39e-fb6318100000</link><description>阿拉伯国家深知，只有以色列是伊朗的瞄准目标，而且其利益没有受到直接威胁，鉴于加沙攻势，阿拉伯国家现在面临着向公众解释其前所未有的联盟的困难</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 09:37:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/arab-states-that-allied-with-israel-and-u-s-for-iran-attack-now-face-consequences/0000018e-eb42-d35c-a39e-fb6318100000</guid></item><item><title>英国和德国高级外交官抵达以色列，以缓和其对伊朗的反应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/british-german-top-diplomats-arrive-in-israel-in-bid-to-temper-its-reaction-to-iran/0000018e-eaef-d35c-a39e-fbef70610000</link><description>卡梅伦和贝尔博克将与几位以色列高级政府官员会面，并警告他们不要进一步升级与德黑兰的紧张局势，此前他们的国家协助以色列挫败了大规模袭击</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 08:41:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/british-german-top-diplomats-arrive-in-israel-in-bid-to-temper-its-reaction-to-iran/0000018e-eaef-d35c-a39e-fbef70610000</guid></item><item><title>耶稣最后的晚餐真的是逾越节家宴吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/was-jesus-last-supper-truly-a-passover-seder/0000018e-eaaa-d35c-a39e-fbeb130d0000</link><description>耶稣祝福了面包还是无酵饼？福音书提供了相互矛盾的答案，引发了圣经之谜</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 08:22:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/was-jesus-last-supper-truly-a-passover-seder/0000018e-eaaa-d35c-a39e-fbeb130d0000</guid></item><item><title>“和平运动失败了”：为什么这位美国福音派人士想要停止武装以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-peace-movement-has-failed-why-this-u-s-evangelical-wants-to-stop-arming-israel/0000018e-e740-db8e-a1bf-ff4f7d080000</link><description>中东和平教会执行主任梅·埃莉斯·坎农牧师博士日益成为美国福音派社区中以色列最大的批评者之一。她解释了为什么本月无法庆祝其联盟成立 40 周年</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 07:37:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-peace-movement-has-failed-why-this-u-s-evangelical-wants-to-stop-arming-israel/0000018e-e740-db8e-a1bf-ff4f7d080000</guid></item><item><title>未能预见德黑兰的战略转变后，以色列必须谨慎行事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-must-tread-carefully-after-failing-to-foresee-tehrans-change-of-strategy/0000018e-e889-d7e3-a9bf-fcbd95670000</link><description>伊朗的导弹和无人机袭击失败了，但以色列高级官员却因回应而陷入困境——回应的时间和性质将由加沙和美国的立场决定。 ■ 地区战争将危及伊朗即将发生的权力交接</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 03:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-must-tread-carefully-after-failing-to-foresee-tehrans-change-of-strategy/0000018e-e889-d7e3-a9bf-fcbd95670000</guid></item><item><title>由于家人警告伊朗局势升级，外国外交官寻求释放以色列人质的新途径</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/warning-that-situation-is-bleak-diplomats-seek-new-path-for-release-of-israeli-hostages/0000018e-e889-d0ca-a99f-fdfbfb100000</link><description>接近会谈的消息人士称，美国最新的提议不够有创意，未能弥合哈马斯和以色列要求之间的差距</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 03:00:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-17/ty-article/.premium/warning-that-situation-is-bleak-diplomats-seek-new-path-for-release-of-israeli-hostages/0000018e-e889-d0ca-a99f-fdfbfb100000</guid></item></channel></rss>